      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, showroom-quality condition, looking and driving just like the day it was first sold. Every detail, from the flawless exterior to the immaculate interior, has been meticulously preserved, making it a rare find for the discerning driver who wants the very best.",
